Package: DeepSeekCell
Title: AI-Powered Cell Type Annotation with Ontology-Aware Reasoning
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2026-04-10
Authors@R: c(
    person("Shu-Lin", "Wang", email = "books@hnu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hunan", "University", role = "cph")
  )
Description: DeepSeekCell is an interactive Shiny application that leverages 
    large language models (DeepSeek and GPT-4o) for zero-shot cell type 
    annotation from single-cell RNA-seq marker genes. The application 
    integrates the Cell Ontology (CL) to provide standardized, biologically 
    grounded annotations with confidence scores and interpretable reasoning.
